# CODEOWNERS for the ascii-art rig.
# Combined with branch protection (require_code_owner_reviews=true), this
# enforces "human approval required" on protected branches — agent reviews
# alone cannot satisfy the merge gate.
#
# Replace $GITHUB_USERNAME with your own handle (or a team like @org/team).
# You are the code owner for the entire repo. Add finer-grained rules below
# if you want different reviewers for docs/, tests/, etc.

# Default owner for everything
*       $GITHUB_USERNAME

# Locked decision records — extra-careful reviews welcome
/docs/decision-records/*    $GITHUB_USERNAME
